summary: This document is a subpoena or warrant request for detailed telephone records associated with Ghislaine Maxwell. keyFacts: The document is a formal legal request (subpoena/warrant) for comprehensive telephone records linked to Ghislaine Maxwell.

The request includes highly detailed information: subscriber data, all call types, session times, payment methods (credit cards, bank accounts), and equipment identifiers.
